text: John C. Rulon House is located in Swedesboro, Gloucester County, New Jersey, United States. The building was built in 1881 and was added to the National Register of Historic Places on November 22, 2000. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Gloucester County, New Jersey ==References== Category:Gothic Revival architecture in New Jersey Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:Houses completed in 1881 Category:Houses in Gloucester County, New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Gloucester County, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places Category:1881 establishments in New Jersey Category:Swedesboro, New Jersey
title: John C. Rulon House
